                            <comment id="14462777" author="harnackf" created="Tue, 8 May 2007 02:11:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch seems to solve the problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks to my colleague Alexej Stojanov. We fixed the issue together.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regards&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Frank&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14477322" author="paulk" created="Tue, 8 May 2007 15:12:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Jochen, let me know if you run out of time to apply this. I am happy to add it and do some testing. Just assign to me if you want, Paul.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14462637" author="blackdrag" created="Tue, 8 May 2007 15:54:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ok, you can apply the patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14477319" author="paulk" created="Wed, 9 May 2007 06:39:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I applied the patch and it definitely fixed the first issue. It doesn&apos;t appear to work properly with colspan however, so I&apos;ll see if I can fix that too before committing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14477323" author="paulk" created="Mon, 14 May 2007 07:23:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch applied plus I added some tweaks to the colspan calculating code (there wasn&apos;t any before) so it works (at least for the simple cases) too now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14477333" author="paulk" created="Sun, 10 Jun 2007 04:01:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No further feedback, assuming fixed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14462714" author="harnackf" created="Mon, 11 Jun 2007 03:34:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Paul,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;thanks for your bugfix.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately we decided not to use SwingBuilder for our little gui and we are to busy to test your additional modifications.&lt;br/&gt;
But we want to use SwingBuilder in the future (1.1-beta-2) to make our ant build scripts more user friendly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regards&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Frank + Alexej &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
